### Create brand
POST {{host}}/catalog/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Nike"
}

###

### List brands
GET {{host}}/catalog/brands?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Search brands by prefix (typeahead)
GET {{host}}/catalog/brands?q=Ni&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get brand by ID
GET {{host}}/catalog/brands/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Rename brand
PUT {{host}}/catalog/brands/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Nike Brasil"
}

###

### Delete brand
DELETE {{host}}/catalog/brands/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### =====================================================================
### Supplier association flow
### =====================================================================

### Step 1 — Login
POST {{host}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("token", response.body.token);
  client.global.set("run", String(Date.now()));
%}

###

### Step 2 — Create brand
POST {{host}}/catalog/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Brand Supplier Test {{run}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("brandId", response.body.id);
%}

###

### Step 3 — Create supplier party
POST {{host}}/party
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "personType": "LEGAL_ENTITY",
  "cnpj": "92303004000167",
  "legalName": "Fornecedor Brand Test {{run}}",
  "customer": false,
  "supplier": true,
  "salesperson": false
}

> {%
  client.global.set("supplierId", response.body.id);
%}

###

### Step 4 — Add supplier to brand → 200 with supplierIds populated
POST {{host}}/catalog/brands/{{brandId}}/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Step 5 — Add same supplier again → 422 (already associated)
POST {{host}}/catalog/brands/{{brandId}}/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Step 6 — Remove supplier from brand → 200 with empty supplierIds
DELETE {{host}}/catalog/brands/{{brandId}}/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Step 7 — Remove supplier again → 422 (not associated)
DELETE {{host}}/catalog/brands/{{brandId}}/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### --- Error cases ---

### Add supplier to non-existent brand → 404
POST {{host}}/catalog/brands/999999/suppliers/{{supplierId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Add non-existent party as supplier → 404
POST {{host}}/catalog/brands/{{brandId}}/suppliers/999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Add party that is not a supplier → 400
POST {{host}}/catalog/brands/{{brandId}}/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
